<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>Aravinda VK</title><link href="http://aravindavk.in/" rel="alternate"></link><link href="http://aravindavk.in/feeds/tag-firefoxos.atom.xml" rel="self"></link><id>http://aravindavk.in/</id><updated>2013-01-25T00:00:00+05:30</updated><entry><title>Firefox OS</title><link href="http://aravindavk.in/blog/firefox-os/" rel="alternate"></link><published>2013-01-25T00:00:00+05:30</published><author><name>Aravinda VK</name></author><id>tag:aravindavk.in,2013-01-25:blog/firefox-os/</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;I was impressed by the demo videos and blog posts about Firefox OS and decided to try it on my phone Nexus S. Searched for Nexus S ROM and found one &lt;a class="reference external" href="http://forum.xda-developers.com/showthread.php?t=1924367"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;. (&lt;cite&gt;TODO: Try building latest version of Firefox OS&lt;/cite&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Installation went smooth, followed the documentation from &lt;a class="reference external" href="http://forum.xda-developers.com/showthread.php?t=1924367"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote class="twitter-tweet"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Installing Firefox OS on my Nexus S. Fingers crossed :)&lt;/p&gt;&amp;mdash; Aravinda (@aravindavk) &lt;a href="https://twitter.com/aravindavk/status/270116962045153280" data-datetime="2012-11-18T10:51:16+00:00"&gt;November 18, 2012&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Booting is superfast and Unicode rendering is awesome, adding new fonts also easy. I just used adb (Android Debugger) to push the font from my system.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote class="twitter-tweet"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Installing fonts is so easy in &lt;a href="https://twitter.com/search/%23FirefoxOS"&gt;#FirefoxOS&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://twitter.com/search/%23kannada"&gt;#kannada&lt;/a&gt; works like a charm :) &lt;a href="https://twitter.com/search/%23mozilla"&gt;#mozilla&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://twitter.com/search/%23nexusS"&gt;#nexusS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;mdash; Aravinda (@aravindavk) &lt;a href="https://twitter.com/aravindavk/status/270149288326221824" data-datetime="2012-11-18T12:59:44+00:00"&gt;November 18, 2012&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;I took screenshots using ADB and ffmpeg.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;./adb pull /dev/graphics/fb0
ffmpeg -vframes &lt;span class="m"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; -f rawvideo -pix_fmt rgb32 -s 480x800 -i fb0 ~/firefoxos_screenshots/s1.png
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
