&lt;p&gt;Used it for a day and changed it back to Cynogenmod since it was not yet ready for day to day use.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hoping to learn more about Firefox OS in &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://wiki.mozilla.org/Engagement/Developer_Engagement/FirefoxAppDays"&gt;Firefox OS App Days&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
